WAP to generate Monthly Weather Report using Constructor,
Destructor.
Create a class named weather report that holds a daily weather report with
data members day_of_month, hightemp, lowtemp,a mount_rain and
amount_snow. Use different types of constructors to initialize the objects.
Also include a function that prompts the user and sets values for each field so
that you can override the default values. Write a menu driven program in C++
with options to enter data and generate monthly report that displays average
of each attribute.
